                    "company": "NSCR",
                    "description": "I am the (co-)project leader in two research projects: \n1) In the first project, we aim to understand whether, and if so how, reparations awarded through international justice procedures contribute to a sense of justice among survivors of massacres and gross human rights violations in Cyprus, Guatemala, Cambodia, and the Democratic Republic of the Congo.  \n\n2) The second research project is funded by the Global Survivors Fund and the Denis Mukwege Foundation. We seek to qualify the effects of Interim Reparative Measures on the daily lives of survivors of conflict related sexual violence in Guinea-Conakry, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, and Yazidis in Northern-Iraq.",
